the final enforcement plan for Uruguay Round market opening, 
which is scheduled on February 15. 
  They declared that they would wage a struggle throughout 
South Korea if their demand were not accepted by the authorities. 
  They warned that the puppet authorities would face a greater 
resistance if the latter dealt with by law those arrested in the 
demonstration on February 1. 

