Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, February 6 (KCNA) -- A joint seminar took 
place in Harare, Zimbabwe, on January 27 to celebrate the 
birthday of the dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il. 
  "The dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il is a great thinker and 
theoretician," "Dear Comrade Kim Chong-il is an illustrious 
leader who has performed undying feats for the Korean revolution 
and the world revolution," and "Dear Comrade Kim Chong-il is a 
