Perish," "On the Fundamentals of Revolutionary Party Building," 
"Abuses of Socialism Are Intolerable" and many other works. 
  Comrade Kim Chong-il, they noted, is an experienced leader 
who has smashed all manoeuvrings of the imperialists with the 
might of singlehearted unity by uniting the popular masses 
around the party and the leader and glorified Korean-style 
socialism and a peoples' leader who deeply loves the people. 
  The speakers were unanimous in saying that Comrade Kim 
Chong-il is an illustrious leader of the era of independence and 
wished him a long life in good health. 

